## <a id="reqs"></a>Requirements

Event Alerts for PCF has the following requirements:

+ Pivotal Elastic Runtime v1.12.x deployed with the following:
  + `Email Notifications` enabled with SMTP server configured.
  + `Notifications Errand` and `Notifications UI Errand` run.

## <a id="limitations"></a>Limitations

Event Alerts for PCF has the following limitations:

+ Only sends email notifications on Healthwatch events.
+ Only sends emails to cf users.

